How do we see whether property is becoming more protected?
Understand
A Property Stewardship Dashboard should show protection, not just ownership.
Metrics may include:
Properties/spaces mapped
 Records checklists completed
 Document days held
 Members educated
 Elders supported
 Youth trained
 Tax reminders sent
 Insurance reviews completed
 Repair needs mapped
 Repairs completed
 Trusted professionals identified
 Property projects active
 Privacy issues avoided
 Stewardship plans created
 Property readiness score
 Reserve balance
 History lessons completed
